This project is a thin orchestration layer. It does NOT redistribute any
third-party code or weights; it fetches them from their licensed sources at
setup time.

Dependencies / upstreams:

- OpenFugu (https://github.com/trotsky1997/OpenFugu), Apache-2.0 — the engine
  (TRINITY router, Conductor DAG executor, OpenAI-compatible server). Cloned
  into vendor/ by setup.sh. Independent reimplementation of Sakana AI's Fugu;
  not affiliated with Sakana AI.

- TRINITY router checkpoint (model_iter_60.npy) and fixture come from
  nshkrdotcom/trinity_coordinator and the associated HuggingFace dataset (MIT).

- Qwen3-0.6B backbone (Apache-2.0), fetched via huggingface_hub.

- The Conductor weights (di-zhang-fdu/openfugu-conductor-3b) are a fine-tune of
  Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct and carry the Llama 3.2 Community License.

The bandit (fugu_swarm/bandit.py) is original code, inspired by the
Beta-Bernoulli routing idea in BicaMindLabs/open-sakanafugu. No code copied.

